'''Lorelei Grace Linklater''' (born May 29, 1994) is a [[Mexico|Mexican]]-born [[American people|American]] actress. She is the daughter of Christina Harrison and director [[Richard Linklater]].<ref>{{cite web|last=Crump|first=Andy|title=‘Boyhood’ International Trailer: Richard Linklater’s Growing Pains|url=http://screenrant.com/boyhood-movie-2014-trailer/|publisher=Screenrant|accessdate=26 April 2014}}</ref><ref>http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2014-07-11/boyhoods-richard-linklater-ive-failed-if-people-just-see-this-as-an-experiment</ref>

== Acting ==
She appears in her father's films ''[[Waking Life]]'' and ''[[Boyhood (film)|Boyhood]]'', the latter playing the older sister to [[Ellar Coltrane]]'s Mason.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailynews.com/arts-and-entertainment/20140424/richard-linklaters-boyhood-was-12-years-in-the-making |title=Richard Linklater’s ‘Boyhood’ was 12 years in the making |newspaper=[[Los Angeles Daily News]] |last=Strauss |first=Bob |date=April 24, 2014 }}</ref>  

== Legal troubles ==
She was charged with cocaine possession and [[Driving under the influence|DUI]] in [[Waco]], [[Texas]] in May 2016.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/richard-linklaters-daughter-gets-deferred-sentence-drug-charge-1016519|title=Richard Linklater's Daughter Gets Deferred Sentence for Drug Charge|website=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|first1=Associated|last1=Press|first2=THR|last2=Staff|date=June 23, 2017|accessdate=September 18, 2017}}</ref> She entered a guilty plea for the cocaine charges and was sentenced to three years [[probation]] in June 2017. The DUI charge was dropped.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.torontosun.com/2017/06/24/richard-linklaters-daughter-lorelei-busted-for-coke-possession|title=Richard Linklater's daughter Lorelei busted for coke possession|website=The Toronto Sun|date=June 24, 2017|accessdate=September 18, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dallasnews.com/news/crime/2017/06/25/boyhood-actress-gets-probation-cocaine-possession-waco|title='Boyhood' actress gets probation for cocaine possession in Waco|website=DallasNews|first=Kylie|last=Madry|date=June 25, 2017|accessdate=September 18, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wacotrib.com/entertainment/actress-placed-on-probation-for-cocaine-possession/article_5523c5ae-dd2e-5128-b0ab-766836587eb4.html|title=Actress placed on probation for cocaine possession|website=Waco Tribune|first=Tommy|last=Witherspoon|date=June 23, 2017|accessdate=September 18, 2017}}</ref>

